@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #90064 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

I'd go with a P-medium for this being a tier-3 target platform, though perhaps we need someone with some context about the specific platform to reproduce or investigate if the mentioned PR https://github.com/rust-lang/backtrace-rs/pull/437 is relevant
I tested the mentioned PR, and it is still failing to build without it.
